section.section:
When a juvenile court enters an order for a child's adoption under this Part III of this subtitle, the juvenile court shall send notice to:
each juvenile court that has a pending CINA case as to the adoptee;
each of the child's living, former parents who has not waived the right to notice;
each living parent's last attorney of record in the CINA case; and
the child's last attorney of record in the CINA case.
